  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 10th Level, you gain the ability to summon and maintain up to two creatures at once. </p><p>Both creatures must remain within 120 Feet of you. </p><p>If you want the second summoned creature to act on your turn the same as the first you must use your action or reaction to command the second creature, instead of a bonus action. </p><p>The second Summoned creature cannot be of the same rank as the current creature summoned. </p>",
